      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved specimen, representing the pinnacle of its class. Maintained to an exacting standard, this vehicle exhibits a showroom-quality finish and flawless mechanical integrity. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering provides an unrivaled driving experience and significant investment potential. Experience the gold standard of automotive excellence.",
